data.text: @nzherald We should be moving down out of traffic light system! isn’t that what we were promised? We all know that ain’t gonna happen tho Ardern hasn’t delivered on a single promise since being elected.
@nzherald You get how this fear porn works yet? You should be afraid when cases rise. Then you should be afraid when they appear to fall because they're not really falling, they're rising.
@Reavers69 @nzherald Only if you're unfortunate enough to have a job in which you cannot WFH.

@nzherald The issue is if you report that you are positive you no longer go to work so you don’t get your normal income and with this government failure to provide proper financial support to everyone no wonder the numbers are going down!!!
@nzherald Anyone can see that this is going to be a twin peak, not a single peak.
@nzherald Great so if you rewrite the rules and deny cases are going down, Jacinda can continue to keep the mandates.
